    <InformationalVersion>1.14.95 (Deploy recovery + WH SKU Investigation polish: (1) The 1.14.86 WhItemsReportService.cs change (IsSlashed bool record field + MAX(CASE) SQL) was stranded in the working tree — never committed. Subsequent commits (1.14.92, 1.14.93, 1.14.94) updated the razor to use r.IsSlashed but the deployed record still had SlashedQty long, causing Azure CI builds to fail with a compile error. Production was stuck on 1.14.91 with the broken Slashed column showing 0s. This release commits the missing service file so the build can finally succeed. (2) WH SKU Investigation column widths: min-width added to every multi-word right-aligned column so labels render on ONE line (HO Price, WH Qty, Stores SOH, Blocked Qty, Blocked Stores, To Fill Qty, Slashed) instead of wrapping awkwardly into two. (3) Includes the previously-pending 1.14.94 Store Summary Merch Need (Month) column.)</InformationalVersion>
